  "body": "Bugfixes:\r\n* Fix old fish version compatibility (#744)\r\n* Fix truncated texts in `--help format` (#745)\r\n* Fix old vulkan-header and libdrm library compatibility (#748, Linux)\r\n* Fix possible segfaults in `--help *-format` (#749)\r\n* Fix invalid resolution detection when using libdrm (Linux, Display)\r\n* Fix segfault when `/sys/devices/system/cpu/cpufreq/` doesn't exist (#750, CPU, Linux)\r\n* Don't detect `SessionLeader` as terminal (Terminal, Linux)\r\n* Fix detection of client IP (Users, Linux)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<details><summary>SHA256SUMs</summary><br>\r\n\r\n```\r\n81ef806890df9fdf858f6e34d8616ce0bd481bf81a50c1a630ecbcec8842c547  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.tar.gz\r\nb7dd32b8a3573ea0e7267dd605a7cb2eb62df00897144298202324b9a499a151  fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64/fastfetch-freebsd-aarch64.zip\r\n6481aa7f8e1709cebe4439e970d340d0040f5064cd755897cd95c31afd0c2417  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.tar.gz\r\nab70bb657e55641b4afee99cc692f89affa742b89163b52c2675a9f3353a873c  fastfetch-freebsd-amd64/fastfetch-freebsd-amd64.zip\r\nbd4dda5f09f09b29c0746031ac470a23b0f3ced15ed118580ed2f164a54a4ae3  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.deb\r\n721c4ae8967427b378acee53aab997bd9e735c21226d3f4aa8f2a179203575ef  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.rpm\r\nc98b9b7a9b5c149836ccb1dd9face518ddbdaddff3cd72d304205901d7e74055  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.tar.gz\r\n263f2263728c13cd01b001ff79a8716a74aa34ed4f5667afa6cbc32afde7b1c6  fastfetch-linux-aarch64/fastfetch-linux-aarch64.zip\r\n5d8ccb80a32154943ea4b4113b2fa900d79dd0ed6f88a5a921028537cff2fe68  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.deb\r\n1340bfa28a2b8262369f2188c63600934c02327f60420160e6d20722f2f030dd  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.rpm\r\n5f3acce6f2536d9e6dd302e1d039f2b38412ed2143a6b337d4b2382f0d6a46f5  fastfetch-linux-amd64/fastfetch-linux-amd64.tar.gz\r\n6f1b9eb762f08684ca19ee44cbfbd5b47d6f25b4cc734209beb7f9c3c23d1a